These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 9

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: thai, indian, american, pakistani
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, fish, lizard, cat
1. the owner of the cat is not to the right of the owner of the goldfish##8
2. the owner of the cat is on the right of the thai##1
3. the indian is on the left or right of the american##3
4. the pakistani is somewhere to the right of the owner of the fish##5
5. the pakistani is not to the left of the owner of the cat##8
6. the owner of the lizard is somewhere to the left of the indian##5
7. the indian is somewhere between the thai and the owner of the fish##7
8. the indian and the owner of the cat have the same parity positions##9
9. the american and the owner of the goldfish have different parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Nationality   | thai | indian | american     | pakistani |
| Pet           | lizard   | cat     | fish | goldfish  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, water, lemonade, mirinda
The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, collecting, skydiving, chess
1. the person who's hobby is writing is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's hobby is chess and the person drinking water have the same parity positions##9
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is not to the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##8
4. the person who's hobby is writing is not to the right of the person drinking mirinda##8
5. the person who's hobby is writing is somewhere to the left of the person drinking juice##5
6. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##5
7. the person drinking water is somewhere to the right of the person drinking juice##5
8. the person drinking mirinda is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage   | mirinda     | lemonade    | juice | water    |
| Hobby      | writing | collecting | skydiving      | chess |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, sprite, water, mirinda
There 4 different types of food: cherry, potato, kiwi, pepper
1. the person drinking water is somewhere to the left of the person eating kiwi##5
2. the person eating cherry is somewhere to the right of the person drinking water##5
3. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person drinking water##1
4. the person drinking sprite is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person drinking water##1
6. the person drinking water is on the left of the person eating cherry##1
7. the person eating cherry is not to the left of the person eating potato##8
8. the person drinking sprite and the person eating potato have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3     |   4   |
| Beverage   | sprite    | water   | almond-milk    | mirinda  |
| Food       | potato | pepper | cherry | kiwi |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  mechanic, architect, doctor, manager
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, d&b, country, ambient
1. the fan folk is the architect##1
2. the fan d&b is on the right of the fan country##1
3. the fan d&b is somewhere to the left of the architect##5
4. the fan ambient is on the left or right of the doctor##3
5. the fan d&b is on the left of the mechanic##1
6. the manager and the fan ambient have the same parity positions##9
7. the doctor is on the left or right of the mechanic##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |       2        |   3    |     4      |
| Job           | manager | doctor | mechanic  | architect |
| Music-Genre   | country             | d&b          | ambient | folk    |

