.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-5::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: rock, pop, soul, reggae
4 different pets are kept: hamster, lizard, mouse, goldfish
1. the fan soul is not the owner of the mouse##6
2. the owner of the hamster and the fan rock have different parity positions##9
3. the owner of the lizard and the fan pop have different parity positions##9
4. the owner of the lizard is somewhere to the left of the fan soul##5
5. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the fan reggae##1
6. the fan pop is not the owner of the lizard##6
7. the fan reggae is somewhere to the left of the fan pop##5
8. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the fan rock##1
9. the owner of the goldfish is not the fan reggae##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| Music-Genre   | rock | soul | reggae  | pop |
| Pet           | lizard   | hamster     | mouse | goldfish      |

