.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-6::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, fantasy, time-travel, disaster
There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, polish, italian, chinese
1. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
3. the italian is somewhere to the left of the person watching disaster movies##5
4. the colombian and the person watching time-travel movies have the same parity positions##9
5. the person watching disaster movies and the colombian have different parity positions##9
6. the italian is not to the left of the person watching epic movies##8
7. the chinese is somewhere to the left of the person watching epic movies##5
8. the person watching fantasy movies is not to the right of the chinese##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy | epic | time-travel | disaster |
| Nationality   | chinese        | italian    | colombian   | polish |

