2. the person who's sport is biathlon is between the person who's sport is cricket and the person who's sport is ice-hockey##2
3. the person who's sport is biathlon and the fan rock have different parity positions##9
4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
5. the fan rock is not to the right of the fan classical##8
6. the fan ambient is somewhere to the left of the fan classical##5
7. the fan rock is somewhere to the right of the fan trance##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |       3       |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | trance    | ambient | rock         | classical     |
| Sport         | cricket | biathlon  | ice-hockey | tennis |

