.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-9::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, card-games, puzzles, camping
4 different pets are kept: lizard, rat, dog, ferret
1. the person who's hobby is photography is somewhere between the owner of the lizard and the owner of the rat##7
2. the owner of the rat is not to the right of the owner of the ferret##8
3. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
4. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
5. the person who's hobby is card-games is not the owner of the lizard##6
6. the person who's hobby is puzzles is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##5
7. the person who's hobby is camping and the owner of the ferret have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | camping | card-games | photography | puzzles |
| Pet     | rat     | dog     | ferret     | lizard    |

