.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-10::.
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, lemon, grapes, grapefruit
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, train, ship, bus
1. the person driving the bus is not to the left of the person eating asparagus##8
2. the person eating grapefruit and the person driving the bus have the same parity positions##9
3. the person driving the train is somewhere to the right of the person driving the ship##5
4. the person eating grapes is on the left or right of the person driving the train##3
5. the person eating lemon is somewhere between the person driving the train and the person driving the bus##7
6. the person eating grapefruit is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food        | grapes | asparagus   | lemon | grapefruit |
| Transport   | ship   | train | jet-ski    | bus      |

