2. the person eating watermelon is on the right of the person eating zucchini##1
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is the person eating blueberry##1
4. the person who's hobby is fishing and the person eating watermelon have different parity positions##9
5. the person eating zucchini is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2     |      3       |     4     |
| Food    | blueberry | orange | zucchini   | watermelon   |
| Hobby   | collecting  | camping   | fishing | rock-climbing |

