.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-13::.
There 4 different types of food: plum, cranberry, raspberry, grapefruit
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, german, indian, mexican
1. the person eating grapefruit is not the mexican##6
2. the mexican is not to the right of the chinese##8
3. the person eating raspberry is not to the left of the person eating grapefruit##8
4. the person eating grapefruit is on the left or right of the person eating cranberry##3
5. the person eating grapefruit is on the left or right of the indian##3
6. the mexican is on the far left##1
7. the chinese is on the left of the person eating raspberry##1
8. the person eating plum is the german##1
9. the person eating grapefruit and the chinese have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |     4     |
| Food          | cranberry   | grapefruit    | raspberry | plum    |
| Nationality   | mexican | chinese | indian   | german |

