.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, cola, 7up, iced-tea
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: colasy, disaster, thriller, horror
1. the person watching colasy movies is not the person drinking iced-tea##6
2. the person drinking iced-tea is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person watching colasy movies##1
4. the person watching disaster movies is in an odd position##4
5. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
6. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
7. the person drinking cola is somewhere to the right of the person drinking iced-tea##5
8. the person watching colasy movies and the person drinking hot-chocolate have the same parity positions##9
9. the person watching thriller movies and the person drinking 7up have different parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage      | iced-tea   | cola  | 7up  | hot-chocolate |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | thriller | horror | colasy      |

