.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, almond-milk, fanta, tea
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, salsa, disco, electronic
 1. the person drinking almond-milk and the fan disco have the same parity positions##9
 2. the person drinking fanta is not to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##8
 3. the fan house is somewhere between the person drinking almond-milk and the person drinking cola##7
 4. the fan disco is somewhere to the left of the person drinking fanta##5
 5. the person drinking fanta is in an odd position##4
 6. the fan disco is not to the left of the person drinking tea##8
 7. the person drinking tea and the fan salsa have the same parity positions##9
 8. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the fan electronic##3
 9. the fan electronic is in an odd position##4
10. the person drinking tea is not to the right of the fan house##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage      | cola  | tea | fanta  | almond-milk |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | disco     | house | salsa     |

