1. the person who's hobby is fishing is somewhere to the left of the person drinking mirinda##5
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is in an even position##4
3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
4. the person drinking juice and the person who's hobby is fishing have the same parity positions##9
5. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
6. the person who's hobby is gardening is the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2      |       3       |    4     |
| Beverage   | iced-tea    | juice | mirinda | lemonade |
| Hobby      | gardening | fishing   | woodworking   | magic-tricks   |

