.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, milk, sprite, almond-milk
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, dancing, collecting, gardening
 1. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 2. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 3. the person who's hobby is gardening is not to the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##8
 4. the person who's hobby is dancing is in an odd position##4
 5. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is not the person drinking milk##6
 6. the person drinking almond-milk is not to the right of the person drinking mirinda##8
 7. the person drinking almond-milk and the person who's hobby is dancing have the same parity positions##9
 8. the person drinking milk is not to the right of the person drinking sprite##8
 9. the person drinking almond-milk is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
10. the person drinking milk and the person who's hobby is dancing have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2       |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage   | milk    | sprite        | almond-milk   | mirinda      |
| Hobby      | gardening | collecting | dancing | filmmaking |

 